1d:T545,This is a benchtop diagnostic instrument for clinical protein analysis in hospital/laboratory settings. Internal evidence shows complete technical specifications (620nm laser LED, dual detection modes, 37°C incubation, multi-sample positions). External tier1_manufacturer sources confirm Meril Diagnostics manufactures diagnostic analyzers and reagents. Tier3_authorized source explicitly identifies 'Meril ProViso Protein Analyzer' as semi-automated specific protein analyzer for laboratory use, confirming product identity. Not an implantable device or consumable - this is capital equipment. Current classification incorrectly states 'Electronic components with optical sensors' which is technically accurate but clinically misleading; should be classified as 'Clinical Chemistry Analyzer' or 'Diagnostic Instrument.' However, the product naming, categorization, and family assignment are all correct. The 'material' field in current_classification is not applicable to diagnostic instruments. Brand field is empty but should be 'Proviso' (product brand) under 'Meril Diagnostics' (manufacturer). Title and description are accurate and clinically appropriate. No conflicts detected between internal and external sources. Recommendation: keep current structure but enrich metadata to clarify this is diagnostic capital equipment, not a component.19:["$","$L1c",null,{"product":{"product_name":"Proviso Semi-Automated Specific Protein Analyzer","product_name_display":"Proviso Semi-Automated Specific Protein Analyzer","sku_code":"PROVISO-001","product_family":"Proviso Semi-Automated Specific Protein Analyzer","product_family_display":"Proviso Semi-Automated Specific Protein Analyzer","slug":"proviso-semi-automated-specific-protein-analyzer","images":[{"id":"f0083ac70185","storage_path":"agile-ortho/products/69c3ed722a7174181a7c3e8d/cover_5dd084c7.jpg","original_filename":"cover_Proviso_Brochure.pdf.jpg","content_type":"image/jpeg","size":755373,"uploaded_at":"2026-03-26T05:58:17.140884+00:00","source":"brochure_extraction","width":3308,"height":2339}],"status":"published","live_visible":true,"brochure_url":"","seo_meta_title":"Proviso Semi-Automated Specific Protein Analyzer | Proviso Biochemistry Analyzers - MedDevice Pro Telangana","seo_meta_description":"The Proviso Semi-Automated Specific Protein Analyzer delivers precise photometric and nephelometric analysis for critical protein diagnostics in hospital lab...","pack_size":"Single unit","size_variables":["250× 244× 138 mm3"],"created_at":"2026-03-25T14:13:06.231548+00:00","updated_at":"2026-03-26T14:44:33.879733+00:00","division_canonical":"Diagnostics","division_live_original":"Diagnostics","category":"Biochemistry Analyzers","material_canonical":"Electronic components with optical sensors","material_live_original":"Electronic components with optical sensors","manufacturer":"Meril Life Sciences","description_live":"The Proviso Semi-Automated Specific Protein Analyzer delivers precise photometric and nephelometric analysis for critical protein diagnostics in hospital laboratories. This advanced diagnostic system features 620nm laser LED technology with dual photodiode detectors, processing whole blood, serum, urine, and citrate plasma samples with automated mixing and 37°C incubation. With 5000 result storage capacity and intuitive TFT LCD touchscreen interface, it streamlines protein analysis workflow for enhanced laboratory efficiency and accurate patient diagnostics.","technical_specifications":{"principle":"Photometry & Nephelometry","testing_method":"Transmission & Scattering of Light","light_source":"620nm Laser LED","sample_type":"Whole Blood, Serum, Urine & Citrate Plasma","positions":"1 test position, 4 sample-prep positions","mixing":"Automated with 3 Different Speeds","incubation":"Automated at 37℃","display":"TFT LCD Touch Screen 3.2\"","communication":"RS 232 Port","storage_capacity":"5000 results","dimensions":"250× 244× 138 mm3","working_voltage":"100-240VAC (≤40W)","detec